parameters:
Za...za...hey! The communication condition isn't
good...⁉

It seems like this building itself is rigged to
interfere with communications...

Za...za...za... Unfortunately, the enemy will
probably recover quickly... Let's retreat...

Is that a child...? Why are they in a place like
this... Don't tell me... That child is also a
product...!?

I found a child! I will protect this one at
least...!

Ahaha! That's not good, Onee-san. You shouldn't
judge people by their appearances.
Where is this...? I, I can't move...
Have you come to, Resistance's Cyborg-san?
Hya, what do you think you're doing...!

Hehehe, why don't you tell us everything about how
the Resistance found out about the auction's
location?

Are you planning to torture me...? It's useless! I
won't say anything...⁉

(W-What's happening...⁉ Normally, something like
this... shouldn't affect me...!?)

Ahahaha! While you were unconscious, Onee-san, I
took the liberty of making some adjustments to
your body~

It's unfair that you have a sensitivity adjustment
function~ As a punishment, I've set your
sensitivity to the maximum.
Guh! Y-You coward...! I'll remember this!

Ahaha! Does it hurt? It hurts, doesn't it? Are you
going to surrender?
Wh...Who would! To the likes of you!

Don't play dumb, it's a dildo. You know what's
going to happen next.

Higgi, it hurts! Take it out, take it out, take it
out!
Ugh, gross... Her womb is popping out.
S-Stop it, I'm going to scream...!

Higgu...! Sh-Shut up! I won't lose... to such...
torture...!
She's not giving in easily, huh!

Come on, if you don't surrender soon, you're going
to lose your hand~
I won't lose... to such... torture...!
Next is your leg, okay? What will you do?

Stop it! Please stop! I can't take it anymore! I
don't want the pain!
Alright then, are you going to surrender?

...Cut off my leg or whatever, I don't care! I
won't give you guys any information!
Hmmm, then as you wish, I'll turn you into a worm.

Who's that? Your boyfriend? I thought you said you
weren't going to talk~?
Come on, just let yourself relax~

Finally awake! This time, I'm going to torment
your womb from the outside.
Hmm~ Where should I poke next~?

Ahhhh! Stop! I surrender! I surrender! Please,
forgive me!

Ahaha! We have plenty of time, so let's take our
time to talk~

Forgive me! Please, I beg you! I'm begging
youuuuuuuu!
